Package: SCE
Title: Statistical Concepts Explorer
Version: 1.2.2
Authors@R: person("Psycholo.ge", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "contact@psycholo.ge")
Description: An interactive Shiny application for building intuition about
    statistical concepts through visualization and simulation. Covers 65+
    modules spanning distributions, inference, modeling, multivariate methods,
    machine learning, and psychometrics.
